<div class="component container" id="how-we-help-you" data-nav-item="">
    <div class="component-content" >

<div class="component c-feature-row-teaser">
    <div class="component-content">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-8 col-md-10 off-md-1 col-lg-12 off-lg-2">
                <h2 class="c-feature-row-teaser__header">
                    How we help you
                </h2>
            </div>
        </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-4 col-sm-8 col-md-10 off-md-1 col-lg-12 off-lg-2">
                    <div class="component accordion c-feature-row-teaser__accordion js-feature-row-teaser__accordion">
                        <div class="component-content">
                            <div>
                                <ul class="items">
<li class="item">
    <div class="toggle-header" tabindex="-1">
        <div class="label">
            <h3>
                Do you know how, why and where your consumers buy and use your products?
            </h3>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="rich-text toggle-content toggle-content--reset">
        <div class="row c-feature-row-teaser__main-content">
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-5 col-f-md-5 col-f-lg-7 c-feature-row-teaser__content-desc">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    Opportunity
                </h4>
                <div>
                    Capture the most detailed picture of what consumers really do: what they watch, what they eat, what they buy, where, when, and how often they buy, which brands they buy, at what price, and why. Through our consumer panels we identify the retailers, people, occasions, categories and trends that will generate sustainable growth for the future, to help you seize the right opportunities.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-3 off-f-md-1 col-f-md-4 col-lg-3 toggle-content__aside">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    How we help
                </h4>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/consumer-shopper-retail/consumer-panels">Consumer Panels</a></span>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/consumer-shopper-retail/consumer-landscape">Consumer Landscape</a></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</li><li class="item">
    <div class="toggle-header" tabindex="-1">
        <div class="label">
            <h3>
                How do you find growth in an omnichannel world?
            </h3>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="rich-text toggle-content toggle-content--reset">
        <div class="row c-feature-row-teaser__main-content">
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-5 col-f-md-5 col-f-lg-7 c-feature-row-teaser__content-desc">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    Opportunity
                </h4>
                <div>
                    People shop everywhere, and they move almost seamlessly between channels. Seizing new growth opportunities means exploring category boundaries, inventing ways of working with new and old retail partners, and closing conversion gaps with target groups or around certain consumption occasions.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-3 off-f-md-1 col-f-md-4 col-lg-3 toggle-content__aside">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    How we help
                </h4>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/consumer-shopper-retail/retail-landscape">Retail Landscape</a></span>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/consumer-shopper-retail/ecommerce">Ecommerce</a></span>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/consumer-shopper-retail/consumer-panels">Consumer Panels</a></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</li><li class="item">
    <div class="toggle-header" tabindex="-1">
        <div class="label">
            <h3>
                Are you presenting the right mix to consumers?
            </h3>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="rich-text toggle-content toggle-content--reset">
        <div class="row c-feature-row-teaser__main-content">
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-5 col-f-md-5 col-f-lg-7 c-feature-row-teaser__content-desc">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    Opportunity
                </h4>
                <div>
                    For maximum brand and category growth, you need to optimise your product assortment, manage promotions carefully, and maximise the return on your in-store merchandising investment. Understanding and measuring success with retailers, channels, missions and occasions is key to this. We can help.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-3 off-f-md-1 col-f-md-4 col-lg-3 toggle-content__aside">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    How we help
                </h4>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/consumer-shopper-retail/retail-landscape">Retail Landscape</a></span>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/consumer-shopper-retail/consumer-landscape">Consumer Landscape</a></span>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/consumer-shopper-retail/shopper-marketing">Shopper Marketing</a></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</li><li class="item">
    <div class="toggle-header" tabindex="-1">
        <div class="label">
            <h3>
                Are you getting the most from your retail partnerships?
            </h3>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="rich-text toggle-content toggle-content--reset">
        <div class="row c-feature-row-teaser__main-content">
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-5 col-f-md-5 col-f-lg-7 c-feature-row-teaser__content-desc">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    Opportunity
                </h4>
                <div>
                    Retailers are a key partner for all product manufacturers, and are facing major disruption. Brands can help retailers find growth by better meeting the needs of consumers and shoppers. Changing social dynamics are creating new store formats and retail models, which require new capabilities and omnichannel skills in order to build better partnerships for mutual growth.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-3 off-f-md-1 col-f-md-4 col-lg-3 toggle-content__aside">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    How we help
                </h4>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/consumer-shopper-retail/shopper-marketing">Shopper Marketing</a></span>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/consumer-shopper-retail/sales-performance-platform">Sales Performance Platform</a></span>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/consumer-shopper-retail/retail-landscape">Retail Landscape</a></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</li>                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    </div>
</div>


